Due to the announced transport strike, classes at FEU Tech will be conducted synchronously online tomorrow, September 18, 2025.

Students are advised to check Canvas accounts and consult faculty for further instructions

Offices will remain open on campus and will follow regular operating hours.

 #TechnologyDrivenByInnovation

Due to the announced transport strike, classes at FEU Tech will be conducted synchronously online tomorrow, September 18, 2025.

Students are advised to check Canvas accounts and consult faculty for further instructions

Offices will remain open on campus and will follow regular operating hours.

 #TechnologyDrivenByInnovation 
 #TheSchoolOfInnovation

message.text:
#TamAnunsyo | As of September 17, 2025, Far Eastern University will strictly implement its Uniform Policy for all students — new, returning, and continuing starting on Monday, September 22, 2025.

Students are required to wear the prescribed school attire and visibly display their FEU ID at all times. 

Kindly refer on the full announcement here:
📎 https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1774J7wzBu/

Stay updated through our TamAnunsyo.

#TamaRiseTogether
#FEUCSO90
